a:2:{s:7:"content";s:1427:"<h2>New York's premier sensory research &amp; product testing facility!</h2>
<p>New York's best-equipped and most-experienced market research facility, designed for focus groups, sensory research and product testing. Features sink booths and food/beverage booths, a test kitchen, focus group room and multi-purpose room. Conveniently located just north of New York City in Westchester County.</p>
<h3>Location</h3>
<ul>
<li>20 minutes from Westchester County Airport</li>
<li>30 minutes from LaGuardia Airport</li>
<li>45 minutes from Kennedy Airport and Manhattan</li>
<li>40-minute train ride from Grand Central Terminal, New York City</li>
<li>Many hotels &amp; restaurants within 5 minutes' drive</li>
<li>Less than 30 minutes from Greenwich, Connecticut</li>
</ul>
<h3>Features</h3>
<ul>
<li>Personal &amp; Home Care Booths (12). Features sink, outlets, sconce lighting with pass-through to product prep area.</li>
<li>Food &amp; Beverage Booths (23). Designed for food/beverage evaluations with pass-through to product prep area.</li>
<li>Multi-Purpose Room (23' x 36'). A totally flexible space, with seating for up to 40 classroom style.</li>
<li>Test Kitchen &amp; Lab (18' x 30'). Walk-in cooler, freezer, six residential ovens, ten microwaves, counter space and more.</li>
<li>Focus Group Room (23' x 36'). Comfortable seating for 15.</li>
<li>Client Lounge. Spacious accommodations with viewing via CCTV.</li>
</ul>";s:12:"content_meta";N;}